Name: UCSB
Description: University of California Santa Barbara is a prestigious school conveniently located adjacent to the beach.

Name: Hermosa Beach Pier
Description: Located in the South Bay of Los Angeles, Hermosa beach pier holds magnificent views of the beach allowing for peaceful strolls near the ocean.

Name: Elysian Park
Description: Elysian Park gives off one of the most unreal views of Downtown LA and is also right next to Dodger Stadium.

Name: SoFi Stadium
Description: Home of the LA Rams and Chargers, SoFi Stadium is the new kid on the block with breathtaking architecture.

Name: The LA Forum
Description: The Forum is a classic venue that holds shows for many famous artists/performers.

Name: Alondra Golf Course
Description: Alondra Golf Course is a favorite among locals which holds two full 18-hole courses, par 3 and 4, along with a driving range.
